author: http://www.nytimes.com/by/matt-apuzzo, https://www.nytimes.com/by/adam-goldman, http://www.nytimes.com/by/michael-s-schmidt
title: F.B.I. Official Wrote Secret Memo Fearing Trump Got a Cover Story for Comey Firing
description: Andrew McCabe documented a meeting that left him concerned that the deputy attorney general may have helped President Trump create a cover story to justify the dismissal.
